Directory structure
===================
   test_4d_qns_general_multipatch           -- executable
   sim4d_qns_general_multipatch_input.nml   -- input file (general)
   circle_mp5_pts12_*.nml                   -- input files (nurbs patches)
   README                                   -- info (this file)
   run/                                     -- output directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, move into it, and copy nurbs input files
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run
     $ cp ../circle_mp5_pts12_*.nml .

1. Run parallel simulation within directory
     $ mpirun -np 4 ../test_4d_qns_general_multipatch ../sim4d_qns_general_multipatch_input.nml

2. Run gnuplot scripts generated at runtime
     $ gnuplot --persist rho_field_multipatch.gnu
     $ gnuplot --persist potential_field_phi.gnu 
